york.Rd

Listed buildings provided by the City of York Council, made available here. This data contains public sector information licensed under the Open Government Licence v3.0: https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/doc/open-government-licence/version/3/.

york

Format

A data frame with seven variables: long, lat, desig_id, bldg_name, grade, status_date, and esri_oid.

long

longitude of the building

lat

latitude of the building

desig_id

ID related to a feature that is not yet known to me

bldg_name

name of the building

grade

one of the three (I, II, III) cateogories of listed buildings

status_date

date the status was made

esri_oid

ID related to a feature that is not yet known to me

For further details, see https://www.york.gov.uk/info/20215/conservation_and_listed_buildings/1346/listed_buildings and https://data.gov.uk/dataset/9417652f-3901-4a16-8368-222deefb36cd/listed-buildings
